sources.name: Available space
sources.query: ts("~sample.disk.space.total", az=${az}, env=${env}) - ts("~sample.disk.space.used", az=${az}, env=${env})

sources.name: Available %
sources.query: 100.0 * (ts("~sample.disk.space.total", az=${az}, env=${env}) - ts("~sample.disk.space.used", az=${az}, env=${env})) / ts("~sample.disk.space.total", az=${az}, env=${env})
